.Sh EXAMPLES
Search for
.Qq optind
as a variable name in the library category:
.Pp
.Dl $ apropos \-tvar \-s 3 optind
.Pp
Search for all manuals referencing the term
.Qq POSIX
in any letter case:
.Pp
.Dl $ apropos \-tall \-I posix
